text.tspan: Share of S. aureus infections resistant to methicillin, 2021

Methicillin is an antibiotic commonly used to treat infections by
Staphylococcus aureus
. This shows the
estimated share of infections by S. aureus in the bloodstream that were resistant to methicillin.
